### Interview Research

**Preparation:**
- Research the subject thoroughly before contact
- Prepare specific questions, not just topics
- Know what you need to confirm vs. discover
- Prepare for reluctance or hostility

**During Interview:**
- Build rapport before sensitive questions
- Use silence strategically
- Ask for documents or other sources
- Get referrals to other sources
- Verify claims in real-time when possible

**After Interview:**
- Document immediately while fresh
- Verify all claims independently
- Follow up on leads provided
- Maintain relationship for future questions

