### Market Sizing

| Approach | Method | Best When |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| Top-down | Total market → segment → target | Market data available |
| Bottom-up | Unit economics × potential customers | Granular data available |
| Value theory | Value delivered × willingness to pay | Novel markets |
| Analogous | Similar market × adjustment factors | Limited direct data |

